    "text": "Apple Inc. (Ticker: AAPL) | Exchange: NASDAQ | Sector: Technology | Industry: Consumer Electronics | Market Cap: N/A | CEO: Timothy D. Cook | Full-Time Employees: 164000 | IPO Date: 1980-12-12 | Country: US | Website: https://www.apple.com",
